body:
I don't know if it's on my side, or Riots side. It's happening multiple times and it's actually getting frustrating!

I go to champion select and when everyone has locked in their champions, sometimes the 2nd window won't even pop up. I'll even log out and log back in but the reconnect isn't even an option. I've reported the bug twice now, despite it happening excessively. It's actually stressing me out cause I'm worried about my account being disabled for "afk" behaviors.

I'm a bit panicked, and honestly I'm hoping something comes of it because its actually really frustrating for me {{sticker:sg-soraka}}
